Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:35.46,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.01,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.59,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.17,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.18,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.10,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.52,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.98,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:03:00.82,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.29,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.79,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:14.13,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.34,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has been separated from his crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and is now hurrying toward Navy HQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.05,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,to stop his brother Ace from being executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.05,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:30.31,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours remain until the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:36.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's combined forces are stationed at Marineford, anticipating the arrival of the Whitebeard Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:42.57,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Ace.  Tell me the name of your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.74,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,My father is Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.86,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:54.79,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother's name is Portgas D. Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:58.66,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,A year and three months after the father's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:03.86,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,a child was born, carrying the blood of the most evil man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.55,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,That child was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:13.51,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:18.39,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,the Pirate King, Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.72,Main,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,So it still lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.95,Main,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:33.55,Main,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The blood of the Pirate King lives on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.54,Main,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,That villain had a child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.40,Main,Reporter 2,0000,0000,0000,,The legend of Gold Roger lives on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.19,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,We can be glad he's been caught, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:09.16,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,If he's the offspring of the Pirate King, then he must be evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:15.13,Main,Slave-trader,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much I could've sold him for, if I'd caught him and put him up at the auction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.66,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This execution is quite the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:24.63,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,So Fire Fist got his strength from his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.15,Main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,Is he after the One Piece as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.01,Main,Man 4,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this is the end for Fire Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:35.00,Main,Man 4,0000,0000,0000,,He's about to disappear from this world, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.25,Main,Hancock,0000,0000,0000,,So he isn't Luffy's real brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.91,Main,Marine 1,0000,0000,0000,,Roger's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.95,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:29.67,Main,Moria,0000,0000,0000,,So his biological son lives on?  What a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:34.60,Main,Moria,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who had a connection to Roger back then should have already been sentenced!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:41.17,Main,Coby,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's Luffy-san's brother, I assumed Dragon was his father, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.50,Main,Helmeppo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so too!  What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.08,Main,Helmeppo,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean they aren't really brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.59,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.96,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.59,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe this, Garp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.95,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,A child's about to be born...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.25,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,My child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:41.41,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I'll have left this world by the time that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:47.01,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you telling this to me, a marine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.31,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:54.15,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,The mother of that child, and any woman with ties to you, will undoubtedly be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.03,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:11.17,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,The government is sure to figure out where I've been this past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.18,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find her, and then they'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:21.26,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,But a newborn child bears no sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:28.39,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Garp!  You and I have nearly killed each other countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:33.78,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you as much as I would a member of my own crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.72,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Protect him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.80,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try that selfish crap on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:56.47,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,No, I know you'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:08.11,Main,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:47.61,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,And you're sure this is the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:53.24,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Roger was spotted here, but he was behaving uncharacteristically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.24,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,He was acting almost like a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.00,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,Roger's era is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.56,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,We must eradicate all traces of his bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:06.95,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,You will investigate every child born during the ten months following his imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.33,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,Investigate all pregnant women, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.93,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,Kill any mother who seems suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.44,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Five children were born this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.95,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,The following are expected to give birth next month...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:36.39,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.30,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,Investigate those with husbands, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.05,Main,Marine cmdr,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.85,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,When our suspicions are cleared, you can have her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:05.19,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.  It's still too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.00,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.84,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.29,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.34,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.09,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:35.45,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet... Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.18,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.06,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,There are no more pregnant women here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.64,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ten months since Roger's capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.81,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there was no child, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:52.36,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,So Roger's age is really over, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:04.86,Main,Doctor,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.52,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,You're Portgas D. Rouge, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:31.31,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a girl, her name will be Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:35.66,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a boy, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.60,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.37,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,This child's name is Gol D. Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.39,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,It's his child... and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.80,Main,Rouge,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.01,Main,Doctor,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.48,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge!  Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.56,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of him, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.36,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.24,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Whose kid is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:48.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:56.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:04.62,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  From now on, this is where you'll be living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:10.35,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be living with these guys.  Try to get along with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.81,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,As annoying as it is, {Copy-paste from episode 422}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.93,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,both me and Luffy carry the blood of a world-renowned criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:25.82,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I owe my mother a debt of gratitude and took the name "Portgas"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:30.18,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't stand the thought that I carry the blood of that worthless father of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.45,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.07,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,My old man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.59,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard. And no one else. {End of copy-paste from episode 422}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:46.30,Main,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Garp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.51,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years now, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:54.42,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Since you took the name of your mother, formed the Spade Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:59.12,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,and ventured to the seas with formidable strength and speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:03.13,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, we finally realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:07.05,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,We had not stopped Roger's bloodline!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:17.82,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,But Whitebeard, who realized it at the same time we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.93,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,decided to raise you to become the next Pirate King,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:26.09,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,and let the son of his old rival on to his own ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.12,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.21,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I got on that ship so I could make the old man the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.65,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who thinks that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:39.70,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,We were careful not to act recklessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.79,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,You were under Whitebeard's protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:50.00,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,But left unchecked, you'd undoubtedly inspire a new generation of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:55.12,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,That is why your execution here today carries such great significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:02.36,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we must go to war against Whitebeard! {So all that to say, what? I'm sure it is comforting to know that your massive potential's about to cost you your head. ??}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.76,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.33,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:18.01,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,The Gates of Justice are opening, but nobody's ordered them to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:20.75,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get in touch with the engine room, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.38,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.00,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they'll open if I just punch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.03,Main,Mr. 3,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we could try knocking on the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.15,Main,Mr. 3,0000,0000,0000,,WAIT!  DO YOU REALLY THINK THEY'LL BE SO ACCOMMODATING?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.64,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,They opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.43,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:58.88,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The Gates of Justice are opening on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:02.68,Main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the Navy said it'd never open for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:09.85,Main,Jinbei,0000,0000,0000,,The engine room is most likely inside Marineford.  Who could have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.71,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!  It is time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.49,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:26.35,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,How?  Because my shoulder blades are dancing a Lambada of rapture!{kae: I'm told this makes no sense in any language. Just deal with it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:31.16,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!  It's coming!  It is time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.25,Main,Prisoner,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Buggy, it can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.29,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.21,Main,Prisoner,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:41.79,Main,Prisoner 2,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized you were actually God's messenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.48,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!  Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.98,Main,Mr. 3,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's not true!  There must be some sort of trick here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:51.15,Thoughts,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,He's right... Who the hell opened the Gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:56.31,Thoughts,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,No...!  Could Heaven itself want to make me the Pirate King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:07.02,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.  Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.07,Main,Hancock,0000,0000,0000,,It is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.45,Main,Doflamingo,0000,0000,0000,,Unnaturally quiet, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.32,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.72,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.16,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.14,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,They appeared so suddenly!  But where did they come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:25.00,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge fleet of pirate ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.35,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Whitebeard?  Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:29.95,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,Douma, the Bohemian Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.83,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Lord McGuy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:34.16,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,The DeCalvan brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.42,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,Whirl Spider Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:42.23,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of these mighty figures... They're all captains renowned throughout the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.96,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,43 ships in all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.56,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't see Whitebeard or his Commanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:51.20,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,But these pirates are definitely allied with Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.48,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see Ace-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.13,Main,Pirate 2,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!  Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:02.37,Main,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get thrown off by this!  You're all hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.70,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,All of you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.96,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we attack them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:11.82,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.  Whitebeard's around here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:15.35,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,He must be waiting for the right time.  Keep your eyes on the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:20.32,Main,Doflamingo,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's getting interesting!  I'm really getting excited here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.47,Main,Doflamingo,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and show up, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:42.29,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:49.66,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:55.10,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he sure picked one amazing place to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.99,Main,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,We never considered this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.71,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shadow beneath the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:11.01,Main,Marine 2,0000,0000,0000,,No way! {kae: srsly, I know it would be against plot-logic, but I'd have totally blasted the fuck out of anything coming up out of the water there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:22.39,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how they did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:27.69,Main,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,They coated their entire fleet and came here along the bottom of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:46.47,Main,Marine,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Moby Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.67,0:23:13.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Moby Dick has surfaced right in the center of Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.28,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,On deck, Whitebeard and his 14 Commanders are lined up for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:20.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeard Pirates head straight for Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.08,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,There is an unbroken bond between them and Ace, as strong as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:26.31,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:27.94,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The Curtain Rises on the Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.71,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Whitebeard's Past
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:32.01,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
